<p>The <b>languages of the African Union</b> are <a href="Language" title="Language">languages</a> used by citizens within the <a href="Enlargement_of_the_African_Union" title="Enlargement of the African Union">member states</a> of the <a href="African_Union" title="African Union">African Union</a> (AU).</p>
